CLASS PROPERTIES & RELATIONSHIPS:

****** RACE ******
A Race has a number.
A Race has a distance.
A Race has a start time.

A Race belongs to a Fleet.

****** BOAT ******
A Boat has a name.
A Boat has a rating.
A Boat has a skipper.

A Boat belongs to many Races
A Boat has many Scores


****** FLEET ******
a Fleet has a name.

A Fleet has many Races.

****** SCORE ******
A Score has points.
A Score has a penalty point (default = 0).
A Score has total points.

A Score belongs to a Race.
A Score belongs to a Registrant.
A Score belongs to a Boat.